About this item

  • 600 WATT POWER: This high powered wireless karaoke PA portable bluetooth speaker is equipped with dual 8" subwoofer and 1" tweeter with 600 watt peak power / 300W RMS at 2.6 ohm for full range stereo sound reproduction and impressive bass response
  • COMPATIBLE WITH BLUETOOTH: The box type loud bluetooth speaker system is compatible with bluetooth for wireless audio streaming and works with devices like iPhone, android mobile phone, iPad, tablet, PC. Ideal for personal indoor home and outdoor use
  • 3 INPUTS: Pyle bluetooth speaker karaoke PA system is equipped with a USB flash drive reader so it can serve as an MP3 player, a 3.5mm AUX input for connecting external devices & a 1/4” mic / guitar input. Equipped with FM radio with digital LED display
  • FLASHING DJ LIGHTS: The bluetooth party speaker with lights features multi-color flashing disco LED party lights. True wireless stereo system adds life to any occasion, great for patio parties & night gatherings when colorful presence is noticeable
  • RECHARGEABLE BATTERY: This Pyle PA speaker is great for karaoke, stage performances & crowd control. It is fully portable, thanks to its built-in rechargeable battery with level indicator lights, and extending carry handle so you can take it anywhere
Note: Products with electrical plugs are designed for use in the US. Outlets and voltage differ internationally and this product may require an adapter or converter for use in your destination. Please check compatibility before purchasing.

    Features: - True Wireless Stereo System - Portable Speaker System - High-Powered PA Loud Speaker Style - Bluetooth Wireless Music Streaming Ability - Multi-Color Flashing LED Party Lights - Built-in Rechargeable Battery - FM Radio with Digital LED Display - Connect & Stream Audio from External Devices - Aux (3.5mm) Input Connector Jack - USB Flash Memory Reader - 6.5mm Microphone input - Battery Level LED Indicator Lights - Rugged & Durable Molded Cabinet Design - Convenient Extendable Carry Handle - For Indoor / Outdoor Use Bluetooth Wireless Streaming: - Built-in Bluetooth for Wireless Music Streaming - Simple & Hassle-Free Pairing - Works with All of Today’s Latest Devices - Smartphones, Tablets, Laptops, Computers, etc. - Bluetooth Version: 4.1 - Bluetooth Network Name: ‘PYLEUSA’ - Wireless Range: Up to 32’ ft.     How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Style: Speaker SystemVerified Purchase
    I bought this speaker for good value and some fun. I knew I was not going to get high-fidelity. I expected the lows and highs were going to be weak or non-existent, and I was not disappointed because I got what I paid for. It is lightweight for its size and thus probably had a puny magnet. I bought it anyways because I just needed something for camping and karaoke. I also bought the Pyle wireless mic kit and it worked perfectly with this speaker, except the echoing was not adjustable on the speaker or mic. Overall, I give it 3.5 stars but had to round it up to 4.
